; 13. Window Title Logger
; Question: Develop a script that runs in the background and logs the titles of all windows that the user switches to, saving the log to a text file.
; Akshat Shetye/AB
#include <File.au3>

$sLogFile = @ScriptDir & "\window_titles_log.txt"
FileDelete($sLogFile)

